{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_bdhkgt_set_1", "eventName": "最後的比武", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "最後的比武", "storyInfo": "截雲想讓鑄劍坊重現之前師父和自己描繪的模樣：有人比武，有人喝酒，大家不分彼此，一同歌唱。正巧，她遇上了兩個醉酒的武人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g5_swordcastingworkshop", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sweep"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個小妹妹，待在這裡幾天了……", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也沒有鬧事，只是在打掃而已，不算違背左將軍的命令。就讓她繼續做吧。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sweep"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這沙子一下子不掃就又積上一層……孟大叔之前，是時時刻刻都在打掃嗎？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$3"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$3"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "武器架、桌子、椅子都修好了，瓦片也貼回去了，爐火也點起來了……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$3"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡看起來，和師父說的一模一樣了。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你找我幹嘛？", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孟大叔走之後，他們說鑄劍坊是你在管了。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……師父生前總會提到這裡，孟大叔也對我有恩，我想讓這裡變回原來的樣子。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們說，我應該來找你。我能來幫忙，打掃、修補，我都會。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，這裡有我收拾就可以了。", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變回原來的樣子有什麼用？不會再有人來這裡了。", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留不住的終究還是留不住。", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲抬起頭，看著這座鑄劍坊。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主人愛惜這裡的一草一木、一桌一椅，器具用了多年都不曾更換，她現在也修好了這裡面所有損壞的物品。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但人來來去去，最終只有自己一個人站在這裡。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不對，還是不一樣，這還不是鑄劍坊。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡應該有人。有打架的人、有喝酒的人……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想問問，除了那個擂台，還有哪裡能找人來打架嗎？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道的話，你們能來和我打架嗎？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然不能。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們知道，哪裡能找人來喝酒嗎？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g1_yumenstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……都說了別喝這麼多，你看你，走都走不穩了！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那又怎麼樣？反正都要走了，多喝點就多喝點……", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你也都看到了，擂台被天災砸塌了，排行榜也不知道被誰收走了……走之前最後看一眼鑄劍坊罷了。", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，看一眼就走吧……你難道還想著宗師、孟大哥還是哪個誰把你叫進去比武嗎？", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們要來和我打一架嗎？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊……？", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿納薩少女站在門口看著兩人，她手上的飛輪和她的眼睛一樣亮。她身後，巡防營的守軍一臉無奈。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你們會武功吧？你們可以和我打架，呃，比武吧？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們特意走到這裡來，就是來比武的吧？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿納薩少女顯然沒有開玩笑。兩個武人看了她一眼後，面面相覷。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經，也有某個眉眼飛揚的女性像她這樣走出來，這樣叫住他們，這樣大聲地說：“快進來，讓我看看你們幾個練功偷懶了沒有！”"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經……"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊——來！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左將軍有令，這裡不得進行任何——哎哎哎，你們——", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g5_swordcastingworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擂台分兩邊，名號報在先。玉門多俠士，豪氣震雲天！在下人稱“玉門二郎拳”張沖——請指教！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，在下“黃沙一字劍”第五十六代傳人林飛沙！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒請教姑娘來自哪門哪派！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$3"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$3"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#11$3"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿……阿納薩，截雲。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#11$3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是幹嘛，怎麼還擺開架勢了？", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#11$3"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼辦？把鬧事的抓起來？", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#11$3"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我去把那兩張椅子移開。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比武的時候，得把擂台上的雜物都清乾淨，不是嗎？", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巡防營守軍默默地撤出兩步外，原本寂寥的小院重新響起揮拳的風聲。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藉著酒意與風中的黃沙，武人欺身而上，雙拳揮擊，試圖壓制住截雲的武器。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，這才對，這才對！擂台比武，四四方方，劃好擂台範圍，乾乾淨淨……", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放屁！要說擂台規矩，你剛才伸手要幹什麼？別以為我不知道你的暗器！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗器怎麼了？暗器也是我實打實辛苦練的！你之前難道沒被我的暗器救過命？", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然是擂台比武，那就不能用暗器！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好好……我不用，那按規矩，比武點到為止，你要在你的劍刃封上松蠟！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我會把我的飛輪也封上。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——再來！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再來！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g5_swordcastingworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾個回合過去，截雲已經看出兩人醉酒，下盤不穩，出手混亂，自己只需要一招就能把他們打出擂台範圍。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個武人眼神越打越清明，越打越正經，彷彿這不是一場醉酒後隨意的較量，而是一場真正的擂台比武……"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使他們的動作已經徹底走形。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不由得放緩了自己的攻勢。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈！就說讓你少喝點酒，這下不行了吧？", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笑什麼？繼續！繼續！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妹妹，比武就要盡興盡力，我看出來了你在讓著我們！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可不行！你得用你的全力！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$3"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#5$3"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——嚇！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#5$3"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——嗚啊！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳……妹、妹妹這一手真漂亮！", "name": "醉酒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！打得好！……呃……", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲擦了擦額頭上的薄汗，爐火很旺，打架很費力氣，所有人都熱得滿臉通紅。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿納薩少女還未從比武中回過神，但她覺得現在就該喝酒了。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們會渴嗎？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烈刀子，你們常喝的酒。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pourwater"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "loop": "false", "channel": "d1", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "loop": "false", "channel": "d2", "delay": 1.6}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，好香，好酒！", "name": "半酣的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們？", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執勤期間，不能飲酒。", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妹妹，別一直舉著了……軍令在身……", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿納薩少女遞酒的手紋絲不動，酒碗裡的烈刀子和她的眼睛一樣清澈。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果他不接，少女大概會一直和他耗著。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——我——唉，好吧。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "師父說，像這樣……請。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒碗相撞，像是多年前那般發出同樣清脆的聲響，潑灑出的酒液浸濕了地上的沙礫。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾人站在鑄劍坊的院子裡，官兵和武人共同舉碗，一仰頭，喝乾了手中的酒。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來，是這個樣子啊……", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿納薩少女突然懂了。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她明白了為什麼玉門人喜歡打架，為什麼大家打完架還能和好如初，一起喝酒。"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她明白了師父為什麼這麼喜歡這裡。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲彎下腰，拾起一小撮地上帶著酒香的沙礫，放進自己隨身的小包中。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "師父，這裡好像，就是你跟我講的鑄劍坊了。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲本想再說些什麼，或者再和大家喝上一碗酒，或者像師父所描繪的那樣，對著風沙和老槐樹唱一首歌……"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，陪你們鬧了這一場，也差不多了。", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊……", "name": "清醒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "末班車隊離城的時間也差不多到了，該走了。", "name": "清醒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走之前還能比這麼一場武，沒白來，沒白來……", "name": "清醒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_npc_797_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妹妹，江湖再見了，別忘了今天的比武，這可是玉門城最後的比武……", "name": "清醒的武人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$3"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“最後的”……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$3"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，欸，你們……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "武人沒有回應她。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩人站起身來，把碗放下，一邊走一邊拍打著身上的塵土，沒有再回頭。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲看著他們的背影，他們走得很穩，彷彿剛剛沒有喝過酒，沒有醉過，剛剛的一切都沒有發生。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼是“最後的”？"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哎，怎麼回事？怎麼打完就走了？", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你剛剛怎麼就讓位置給他們了？你真不怕他們酒後鬧事？", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒看到他們放在門口的行囊嗎？我認得他們兩個。他們本來就是外面來的，這次離開玉門，就回老家了。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是最後一次了，他們只是想在這裡比一場，那就比上最後一場吧。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留不住的終究還是留不住。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過……他們今天打得真的很盡興。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔……", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來是這樣的。"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留不住的終究還是留不住。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g6_yumengate", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一日後"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲，鑄劍坊的事情……", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……道理沒有說錯，但那天在鑄劍坊，我的話說得太重了……", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唉，你要不要留在玉門？", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這裡有不少老友，不論你想做點什麼，總能找到一個讓你落腳的地方的。", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#9$3"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "師父都已經放下了，我也在這裡真正地打了一架，很盡興。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#9$3"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也準備離開這裡了。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算去哪裡？", "name": "荊先生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_799_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截雲沒有回答，她走出了玉門城門，慢慢地唱起了一首歌。"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g11_yumendesert", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽落下，明早還從東邊升起來♪", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月亮升起，明早會從西邊落下去♪", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈壁上面的裂紋長滿了，會有來年的雨水滋潤它♪", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沙漠深處的沙拐棗枯死了，會有地下的泉水救活它♪", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一陣狂風刮過，夾帶著從沙渠翻湧出來的滾滾黃沙，遮住了截雲遠去的背影。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想看看江南，也想去嚐嚐菱角，見見師父說的那些，江湖上的人。", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想……自己四處走走，看看。", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看什麼才是真的可以讓我像師父那樣，記很久很久的人和事。", "name": "截雲"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g3_yumenobservationtower_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左將軍，我們來領罰。", "name": "巡防營守軍A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_795_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天值勤期間擅自飲酒，按照軍律，當罰軍棍。", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封條也已經寫好了，左將軍，關鑄劍坊的事……？", "name": "巡防營守軍B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這種事情，不需要再來問我了。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們那時自己喝了那碗酒，你們可以自己做這個決定。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}